tress)|Roja]] || Telugu |- |21 ||1999 || ''[[Samarasimha Reddy]]'' || Nandamuri Balakrishna, [[Anjala Zaveri]], [[Simran (actress)|Simran]], [[Sanghavi]] || Telugu |- |22 ||2000 || ''[[Ravanna (film)|Ravanna]]'' || Dr. Rajasekhar, [[Soundarya]] || Telugu |- |23 ||2000|| ''[[Vamsi (film)|Vamsi]]'' || Mahesh Babu, [[Namrata Shirodkar]] || Telugu |- |24 ||2001 || ''[[Narasimha Naidu]]'' || Nandamuri Balakrishna, Simran, [[Preeti Jhangiani]]|| Telugu |- |25 ||2002 || ''[[Allari Ramudu]]'' || [[N. T. Rama Rao Jr.]], [[Aarthi Agarwal]] || Telugu |- |26 ||2002 || ''[[Indra (2002 film)|Indra]]'' || Chiranjeevi, Aarthi Agarwal, [[Sonali Bendre]]|| Telugu |- |27||2003 || ''[[Palanati Brahmanaidu (film)|Palnati Brahmanaidu]]'' || Nandamuri Balakrishna, Aarthi Agarwal, Sonali Bendre || Telugu |- |28 ||2004 || ''[[Adavi Ramudu (2004 film)|Adavi Ramudu]]'' || [[Prabhas Raju Uppalapati|Prabhas]], Aarthi Agarwal || Telugu |- |29 ||2005 || ''[[Narasimhudu]]'' || N. T. Rama Rao Jr, [[Ameesha Patel]], [[Sameera Reddy]] || Telugu |- |30 ||2009 || ''[[Maska (film)|Maska]]'' || [[Ram Pothineni|Ram]], [[Hansika Motwani|Hansika]], [[Sheela (Tamil actress)|Sheela]] || Telugu |- |31 ||2017 || ''[[Aaradugula Bullet]]'' || [[Gopichand (actor)|Gopichand]], [[Nayanthara]] || Telugu |}
