{{about|subsections of nightclubs|room used for photography|darkroom}} 
{{Unreferenced|date=March 2008}}
A '''darkroom''' or '''dark room''' is a darkened room, sometimes located in a [[nightclub]] or [[sex club]], where sexual activity can take place.  When located in bars, dark rooms are also known as '''backrooms''' or '''blackrooms'''. Some dark rooms incorporate black, blue, or red lights.

